The paper deals with facial attribute recognition using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the issue of inconsistency among attributes computed from multiple images, which could be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of annotations and correction of incorrectly annotated labels, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
